From 32bf30e9d4b7f014fad3f54ae11d93286612ae9b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Konrad Weihmann <kweihmann@outlook.com>
Date: Sat, 28 Feb 2026 07:12:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] httpclient: adapt to IRB changes

IRB.irb_at_exit is now called IRB.conf[:AT_EXIT].

Upstream-Status: Pending
Signed-off-by: Konrad Weihmann <kweihmann@outlook.com>
---
 bin/httpclient | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/bin/httpclient b/bin/httpclient
index 57d3f3e..e7cd21a 100755
--- a/bin/httpclient
+++ b/bin/httpclient
@@ -65,7 +65,7 @@ class Runner
         irb.eval_input
       end
     ensure
-      IRB.irb_at_exit
+      IRB.conf[:AT_EXIT]
     end
   end
 
